System:

    melt of 1500 chains of 4 atoms, with angle and dihedral potentials.

    Requires a version of mcSim compiled with angles (option -a) 
    and dihedrals (-d) enabled.

Usage
----- 

Here mode = nve or nvt

MC simulation:

    mcSim -e -p param.mode -c commands.mode

Restart and extend previous simulation

    mcSim -e -r restart -c commrst.mode -o rst
